@startuml
autonumber
actor User
participant "CV Parser" as CVParser
participant "Screening Question Manager" as ScreeningQuestionManager
participant "Rating Generator" as RatingGenerator
participant "CV Comparator" as CVComparator
participant "ChatGPT Validator" as ChatGPTValidator
participant "User Interface" as UserInterface
UserInterface ->> CVParser : Submit CV
CVParser -> CVComparator : Parse CV and extract key information
CVComparator -> RatingGenerator : Calculate CV ranking score
CVParser -> RatingGenerator : Calculate CV ranking score
ScreeningQuestionManager -> RatingGenerator : Calculate screening question validation score
ChatGPTValidator -> RatingGenerator : Calculate screening question validation score
UserInterface ->> ScreeningQuestionManager : Present screening questions
ScreeningQuestionManager -> ChatGPTValidator : Validate applicant responses
ChatGPTValidator -> RatingGenerator : Calculate screening question validation score
UserInterface ->> ChatGPTValidator : Submit applicant responses
UserInterface ->> CVComparator : Compare CV with job requirements
CVComparator -> RatingGenerator : Calculate CV ranking score
UserInterface ->> RatingGenerator : Display rating results
@enduml